Scenario Description: Customer Order Invoice

Purpose: This scenario generates an HTML invoice for each customer based on XML order data. Each invoice includes customer details, ordered items, total price, and delivery date.

Formatting Addresses: The updated XML format assumes the address is a single string, so the XSLT code outputs it directly without additional concatenation.

Clickable Email Links: The XSLT stylesheet ensures that email addresses are displayed as clickable links for easy access.

Functionality: The XSLT stylesheet transforms XML data into a well-organized HTML document. Customer addresses are presented as single, formatted strings for clarity, and email addresses are clickable. Headers separate each customer’s invoice, making the document readable and well-structured for both printing and online viewing.

The final HTML document is designed to present the information clearly and professionally, suitable for use as an invoice.
-->

